data.description: Welcome to this charming and updated split-level home nestled at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, offering a perfect blend of comfort, style, and tranquility. This residence is a true gem, boasting a range of features that make it an ideal haven for families and individuals alike. Enjoy the sense of community and privacy that comes with residing on a quiet street, making it an excellent choice for those seeking a peaceful retreat. The split-level design of this home not only adds architectural interest but also enhances the functionality of the space. The distinct levels create defined living areas, allowing for a seamless flow between rooms. This layout provides a sense of openness while still maintaining a cozy and intimate atmosphere. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your dream home – schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort that await within these walls.
